{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act45side", "eventName": "無憂夢囈", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SS-6", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "回聲飄蕩的大廳", "storyInfo": "祥子回到家中，發現原本酗酒的父親竟然正在家裡熱情地準備飯菜。更讓她沒有想到的是，在這個夢裡，自己的母親沒有去世。時隔多年，祥子再次見到了自己的“母親”。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g1_victoriavillage", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愛麗絲姐姐，還有貝娜姐姐——！", "name": "激動的孩子們"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_369_bena_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有遵守約定帶糖果給你們哦，每個人都有份！", "name": "貝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_369_bena_1#6$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好耶——", "name": "激動的孩子們"}, "figure_art": "avg_369_bena_1#6$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_369_bena_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你們有按照約定，想好自己心裡重要的東西嗎？", "name": "貝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_369_bena_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的是存錢筒！你聽，裡面都是存下來的硬幣！", "name": "激動的孩子A"}, "figure_art": "avg_369_bena_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我之前種出來的小花……很好看，所以想讓貝娜姐姐幫忙保存。", "name": "激動的孩子B"}, "figure_art": "avg_369_bena_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_369_bena_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好好好，大家來排隊——一個個來！", "name": "貝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_369_bena_1#6$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愛麗絲和貝娜嘗試讓孩子們依序介紹他們心中的珍視之物，但似乎每個孩子身上都散發著無限的熱情。"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "稚嫩的童聲此起彼伏，眼下的光景卻絲毫不見混亂，反而充滿了溫馨。"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_243", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是祥子嗎？", "name": "和善的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼突然回來了？", "name": "和善的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t請問你是……？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_290_vigna_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們最近剛好在這附近出外勤任務，我就帶祥子一起過來了，順便讓她回家看看。", "name": "紅豆"}, "figure_art": "avg_290_vigna_1#8$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_243", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你爸每天都有提到你呢，說你在一家大公司實習，忙到都沒時間回信。", "name": "和善的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就沒看過他講這麼多話的時候，看來他是真的想你了！", "name": "和善的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你快點回去吧，給他一個驚喜，然後好好安慰他一下！", "name": "和善的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_290_vigna_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t（小聲）祥子，你從剛才就很奇怪……感覺你的反應老是慢半拍！", "name": "紅豆"}, "figure_art": "avg_290_vigna_1#11$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t請問……我家在哪裡？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_290_vigna_1#11$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_243", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……？", "name": "紅豆&和善的鎮民"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g1_victoriavillage", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然之後的對話異常尷尬，但祥子還是按照好心人的指引，順利地找到了回家的路。"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "順著蜿蜒的小路，她終於走到了自己“家”門前。那是一棟潔白的、陌生的房子。"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "庭院裡的花草被修剪得整整齊齊，她能聽見花壇裡澆水設備發出的細微聲響。屋頂的煙囪冒出一縷縷炊煙，屋主正在準備今日的午餐。"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她知道，自己即將前往的，並不是真正的“家”。"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她真正的家，在遙遠而不可及之處。"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "提到家，祥子會先想起豐川家的宅邸，然後是那個有著一股酒氣、飄散著灰塵的小小的租屋處。"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她想起了那個曾經誠實勤奮的父親。"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜真正的父親，現在或許正提著酒瓶，遊走在街頭。也許他會提到自己的名字，但搭配的修飾詞絕無可能與“美好”有關。"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，這才是豐川祥子的現實。"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而眼前的這些是莫菲絲為她創造的夢境，也是用來囚禁她的牢籠。"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g5_sakikodininghall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一股食物的香氣撲鼻而來。"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼哼——♪哼哼哼——♪哼哼——♪哼哼哼——♪", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#2$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……祥子？！", "name": "“父親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#2$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼突然回來了？不是說在公司工作很忙嗎？", "name": "“父親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#2$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t嗯……剛好有外派任務，所以回來看看。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也不常寄信回來，我每天只能翻來覆去的看你以前寫的信。", "name": "“父親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#6$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t普通的信而已，也沒有必要……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寶貝女兒寄回來的信，哪是什麼普通的信！", "name": "“父親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#6$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t父親，好像有什麼東西燒焦了……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "“父親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#2$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "稍等我一下！", "name": "“父親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#4$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 4.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_meatbakingtray", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_makesoup", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_soup", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#3$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "忘記注意時間了……這下只能重做了……", "name": "“父親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#3$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了能做出祥子喜歡的料理，我專門去學了一段時間，你不想吃吃看嗎？", "name": "“父親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t父親，你以前不是不煮飯的嗎？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在日子比較悠閒，有空的時候就研究點新東西。", "name": "“父親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#6$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且你的臉都瘦成這樣了……", "name": "“父親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#3$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t羅德島有定期健康檢查——我的體重還是和以前一樣，沒有變化。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一定瘦了！", "name": "“父親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#3$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“父親”心疼地伸出了手，摸了摸女兒的頭。"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……？", "name": "“父親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#5$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "父親的手讓她感到既陌生又熟悉。"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記憶中她總是彎下腰，將爛醉的父親的手臂搭在自己的肩膀上，然後半步半步地往家的方向走去。"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的手總是無力地垂在她眼前，就像剛才那樣近在咫尺，卻又那麼不同……"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是小孩子了，不要這樣……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對我來說，祥子永遠都是我可愛的女兒。", "name": "“父親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#5$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使出去工作了，也不能忘記保持笑容哦~", "name": "“父親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#5$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#13$2"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "父女兩人面對面地笑了起來，剛才的猶豫也全被祥子拋在了腦後。"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她能確信，自己現在正發自內心地笑著。"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_smoothpiano", "volume": 0.2}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 4.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "樓上為什麼會有鋼琴聲……今天家裡有客人嗎？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？祥子，你在說什麼啊？", "name": "“父親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#2$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然是瑞穗在房間練琴啊。", "name": "“父親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#2$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……媽媽？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，那架鋼琴一直以來不是都只有你和瑞穗可以彈嗎？", "name": "“父親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#5$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對哦，祥子回來了，還沒跟瑞穗說呢。", "name": "“父親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#5$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1940_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果她看到你了，一定會很高興，你趕快上去吧！", "name": "“父親”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1940_1#5$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g5_sakikodininghall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.7, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雙腿發軟。"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "腦中持續不斷地嗡鳴。"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodenstairfts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_piano_start", "volume": 0.1}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鋼琴。"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在鋼琴聲中，關於媽媽的記憶慢慢湧上心頭。"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子記得，舉行媽媽的葬禮那天，她哭得很傷心。"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodenstairfts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_smoothpiano", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽最愛的樂器就是鋼琴，所以祥子也喜歡鋼琴。"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她會輕輕地握住祥子的手，教她摸索鋼琴上的每一個黑白鍵。"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在媽媽離開後的日子裡，祥子依然清晰地記得兩人相處時的每一個細節，並常常一遍接一遍地彈奏媽媽教給她的每首曲子。"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodenstairfts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "逃吧。"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一切都是虛假的，一切都只是莫菲絲創造的夢境。"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不是真正的媽媽。"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫菲絲怎麼可能瞭解她的一切？"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是低劣的偽造品。"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是。"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是——"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "腳步根本沒有停下來的意思，甚至越來越快。"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使這是夢境，即使她是“偽造品”。"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "65_i09", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她就這樣，真實地出現在了眼前。"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她就坐在那裡，沉醉在自己的演奏中。"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "窗外的光線打在她的身上，讓她的身影有些難以分辨。"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而此時此刻，祥子心中只有一個想法——"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t媽……媽媽……？", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“母親”停止了演奏，她轉過身。"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……祥子？", "name": "“母親”"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼前的一切，是那麼地真切。"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g10_dreamcastlestage", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>一生飛翔的羽獸，並非不願降落於陸地。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>堅韌的雙翼，掩飾的是無足的苦痛與悲劇。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>我，毋畏遺忘。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}